body:
When i use callbacks meet some wrong, run my program output"InvalidArgumentError (see above for traceback): You must feed a value for placeholder tensor 'conv2d_3_input' with dtype float and shape [?,28,28,1]
	 [[Node: conv2d_3_input = Placeholder[dtype=DT_FLOAT, shape=[?,28,28,1], _device="/job:localhost/replica:0/task:0/device:CPU:0"]()]]"

my code includes callbacks as below:
tbCallback=keras.callbacks.TensorBoard(log_dir='./mygraph', 
                                       histogram_freq=1,write_graph=True,
                                       write_grads=True,write_images=True)

history=model.fit(train_x,train_y,
          batch_size=batch_size,callbacks=[tbCallback],
          epochs=epochs, verbose=1, 
          validation_data=(test_x, test_y))  

when i change histogram_freq=0, then it can work. but no data be shown in tensorboard.
when histogram_freq=1 or 2, the program can work just on first time, but no data shown in tensorboard.  I am so sad for this, hope your help!
